  "description": "<h4>Application:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Compatible with 2005-2014 Ford Mustang All Models (Except Billet, Shelby, GT500, Cobra &amp; Mach I)</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Package Includes:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>2 Front Springs</li>\n<li>2 Rear Springs</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Features:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>They will lower your car approximately 1.5\" while giving you a good ride quality</li>\n<li>These springs are rated at approx 650lb front and 250lb in the rear</li>\n<li>They will give you the handling you need for spirited road and track use</li>\n<li>Springs are slightly stiffer than stock, while they retain excellent ride comfort</li>\n<li>Excellent all around lowering spring for street use and racing</li>\n<li>Get the looks and functionality of a lowering spring with OEM quality</li>\n<li>Compatible with OEM and aftermarket struts or shocks, NO special parts or hardware will be necessary for upgrade</li>\n<li>High quality Blue powder coated finish for a custom look</li>\n<li>The accessories in the photos are included</li>\n<li>1 year warranty for any manufacturing defect</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Technical Specifications:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Drops Approx. 1.5\" Front, 1.5\" Rear</li>\n</ul>",
